data.name: customSqlQuery3.Sql
data.value: SELECT WarehouseCode, RTRIM(LTRIM(UPPER(Description))) + '(' + RTRIM(LTRIM(UPPER(WarehouseCode))) + ')' AS Description, ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY WarehouseCode) AS Ord FROM Masterfile.Warehouse WHERE ISNULL (IsInactive, 0) = 0 GROUP BY WarehouseCode, Description UNION ALL SELECT 'ALL' WarehouseCode ,'ALL' AS Description, 0 AS Ord ORDER BY Ord

data.name: customSqlQuery4.Sql
data.value: SELECT BizPartnerCode, RTRIM (LTRIM (UPPER (Name))) + '(' + RTRIM (LTRIM (UPPER (BizPartnerCode))) + ')' AS Name, ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY BizPartnerCode) AS Ord FROM Masterfile.BizPartner WHERE ISNULL (IsInactive, 0) = 0 GROUP BY BizPartnerCode, Name UNION ALL SELECT 'ALL' BizPartnerCode ,'ALL' AS Description, 0 AS Ord ORDER BY Ord
